                <note rend="inline" type="source">817.00/2606: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Nicaragua</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Jefferson</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Acting Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Managua</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1919-06-25T14:00:00-05:45">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 25, 1919, 2 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[<hi rend="italic">Received June 26, 3.11 a.m.</hi>]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Referring to my cable of June 9th, 11 a.m. Mr. Canton within the next 10 days
                    expects to arrive at Bluefields to assume duties.</p>
                <p>Now that matters have been placed in his hands, I do not believe that there will
                    be any difficulty in the prompt and satisfactory settlement of the pending
                    question including expulsion decree.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Jefferson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
